metadata.name: Josefina, La Re₿olucionaria
metadata.description:
"Josefina, La Re₿olucionaria" - Digital, 2022

What else can you think of, if not a ₿itcoin and Ξthereum art revolution, when thinking of Josie Bellini? 

When Josie approached me to make a personal commission art piece for her I was both honored and stressed out. A strong woman is seen riding the wall street bull in a rather detrimental state, as if she has tamed it, signaling the start of a revolution.

Thank you, Josie.
